1
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,920
Oh, great Dragon God

2
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:15,160
We acknowledge here that we have strayed from your path

3
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:19,840
Please reflect upon us with your clear Dragon's Eye

4
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,560
My Lord

5
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:21,800
The time has come

6
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,440
Bring up the sacrifices

7
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,600
Dragon God above

8
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:31,120
Please enjoy this offering

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,200
You have toiled all day today

10
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,160
Rest early

11
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:50,040
I will come for you tomorrow morning

12
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,640
Fire!

13
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,880
Fire!

14
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,840
Fire!

15
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:55,560
Fire!

16
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,160
That is...

17
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,080
The Commander's Residence

18
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,760
Stop right there

19
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,880
Who goes there?

20
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,560
I am Li Jing

21
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,160
Greetings, Garrison Commander

22
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,480
Sacrificing children and pregnant women to an evil god

23
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,840
Xu Zhong, have you no humanity left?

24
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:49,120
The Dragon God grants you liberation

25
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,960
Kill them

26
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,400
Yu Han, take the children and leave first

27
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,640
Go, quickly!

28
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,640
How dare you! Kill that woman!

29
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:19,080
It's all over

30
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:34,680
The Dragon God has his own plans

31
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:37,480
The Divine Will cannot be defied

32
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,280
My child is still inside

33
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,480
You fiend

34
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:03,640
Heaven and earth may collapse, but the Dragon God cannot be profaned

35
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,760
Sun and moon may fall, but the Dragonflame cannot be extinguished

36
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,880
Stop the ritual immediately

37
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,840
Kill me

38
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,120
No one can stop the Dragon God

39
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:28,280
Burn my broken body, the Dragonflame shall not die

40
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,800
The Dragonflame shall not die

41
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,280
What are you staring at?

42
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,640
That Fire Serpent has escaped

43
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,840
Think of a way to deal with it, quick

44
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:35,640
Okay

45
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,600
Be careful yourself

46
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,720
Elements of the four directions

47
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,560
Cleanse this space

48
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:28,760
The Dragon God wants her dead

49
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,320
Wait a moment

50
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,440
Xu Zhong has lots and lots of treasure

51
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,160
I know where he hides his money

52
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,160
Why don't we all split his wealth?

53
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,040
Witch

54
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:47,480
We are pure Believers of the Dragon God

55
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,600
Return to the embrace of the Dragon God

56
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,320
Do not hurt Yu Han

57
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,200
Dad

58
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,440
Li Jing

59
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,080
Li Jing

60
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,680
Don't be in such a hurry to fight

61
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,360
It's dangerous here

62
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:16,840
You go first

63
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,800
Listen to me

64
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:20,240
This Fire Serpent is immune to physical damage

65
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,040
What do you mean?

66
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,360
You can only shatter it

67
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,600
You can't kill it

68
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,720
Then what do you suggest?

69
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,080
What do you mean "what do you suggest"?

70
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,080
You ask me, who do I ask?

71
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,040
That's it

72
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,520
The Chentang Pass Grand Formation
